  "starting_equipment_derivation": {
    "method": "AiG does not provide explicit starting equipment lists. Starting gear is derived from:",
    "steps": [
      "1. Roll starting money per culture formula",
      "2. Determine social class (Mythras Core p.21-24, culture-appropriate table)",
      "3. Character receives weapons from their chosen combat style",
      "4. Armour and other equipment purchased from starting money using Mythras Core equipment prices (p.69-72)",
      "5. Cultural technology level constrains available materials (e.g., Balazaring: stone/wood; Sartarite: bronze; Lunar: bronze/some iron)"
    ],
    "attestation_note": "This derivation method is attested by AiG p.24-25 ('Determine Starting Money and Equipment') which gives only the money formula and directs players to purchase equipment. The combat style weapons are the character's starting weapons per standard Mythras character creation (Core p.33: 'Characters begin with weapons and a shield as noted in their Combat Style')."
  },
  "validated_at": "2026-05-21",
  "validation_method": "Pre-Magic PDF validation plus CSE supersession for combat styles.",
